{"tid":684251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[詳文分析] 拉莫斯弄傷沙拿那一下是柔道比賽也禁用的「脇固め」","createTime":"2018-05-30T11:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T14:59:26.000Z","uid":55851,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"870c63619387e5a5fdb3eac8f780cb3e424c8dfa","tid":684251,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"一開始利申，我是利迷。歐聯決賽本來是一場大戰，但拉莫斯這一下動作卻令沙拿受傷，令比賽失色，這種流氓行為更是令人憤怒。嬲當然嬲，但也跟大家說一下當中的技術，以及解釋一下我為什麼覺得拉莫斯是有心的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9TKlUtn-M8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9TKlUtn-M8s&d=t4%2BpoORVBe1nBgduCQe%2Fkf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6ea03cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9TKlUtn-M8s</a><br />\n<br />\n這一下用腋下夾著別人的手再壓的技術，在柔道中叫「脇固め」或「腋固め」(Waki-Gatame )。<br />\n在柔道中，在站立時使用腕挫腋固，再把對手帶進地面是會被即時判敗的，更是連試都不可以試（To fall directly to the Tatami while applying or attempting to apply techniques such as Ude-Hishigi-Waki-Gatame），因為這一招太容易令人脫臼。這招很快，狹著對方所以很難逃脫，而且把身體所有的重量都放在對方的關節上，很容易弄傷對手。<br />\n看看以下片段就明白，這是2012 European Championships Chelyabinsk的比賽：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EuA5O6rYxOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEuA5O6rYxOc&d=t4%2BpoORVBe1nBgduCQe%2Fkf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=59548408\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EuA5O6rYxOc</a><br />\n<br />\n是不是似曾相識？當然了，就正是拉莫斯那一招嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UxCcZe_q1iI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUxCcZe_q1iI&d=t4%2BpoORVBe1nBgduCQe%2Fkf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=753a80a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UxCcZe_q1iI</a><br />\n<br />\n為什麼我覺得他有意弄傷沙拿，在於摔時身體的轉動，而非誰先勾手。向前仆的時候身體轉動，加上夾緊沙拿的手，令背及身體重量都壓在沙拿的手上，這樣的轉動必要嗎？<br />\n而這並不只是我個人覺得，歐洲柔道聯盟也是這樣看：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1491327/org/1f77bf57377358c97bf1144b9a6c7c78.JPG/dt-eBosiJ-qmJvYkJOn6j34-3NqVbo-3kKSrN5Ckqzc?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1491327%2Forg%2F1f77bf57377358c97bf1144b9a6c7c78.JPG%2Fdt-eBosiJ-qmJvYkJOn6j34-3NqVbo-3kKSrN5Ckqzc%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=a4f61d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輸不是問題，那有球隊沒輸過(而這次輸很大程度上是龍門「派膠」，唉)。問題在於蓄意弄傷其他球員的行為，就算是嘗試也不應該，世上有良知的人也會讉責及唾棄這種行為，就算利物浦的球員這樣做我也會罵。<br />\n最後，如果覺得我bias、覺得我酸的話whatever，可以留言回應。以武論武，我就是這樣寫的了。<br />\n今次係咁多！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%AD%A6%E5%82%99%E5%BF%97/193557/%E6%AD%90%E8%81%AF%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD-%E6%8B%89%E8%8E%AB%E6%96%AF%E5%BC%84%E5%82%B7%E6%B2%99%E6%8B%BF%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%8B%9B?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=martialabhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BF%2597%2F193557%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD-%25E6%258B%2589%25E8%258E%25AB%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25BC%2584%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%25B2%2599%25E6%258B%25BF%25E9%2582%25A3%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%258B%259B%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmartialabhk&d=t4%2BpoORVBe1nBgduCQe%2Fkf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6653a48a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%AD%A6%E5%82%99%E5%BF%97/193557/%E6%AD%90%E8%81%AF%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD-%E6%8B%89%E8%8E%AB%E6%96%AF%E5%BC%84%E5%82%B7%E6%B2%99%E6%8B%BF%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%8B%9B?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=martialabhk</a>"},{"pid":"878671ad141aaaa1cda0cc82aa0e988e47d74e53","tid":684251,"uid":51171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:51:16.000Z","msg":"根本睇拉膠落地個勢係應該右邊膊落地先，但條仆街就夾住球王夾硬用力扭向右紮落去，變成左邊身落地，球王右膊冇俾佢屈斷已經算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb40fbbfcb25e8aab868033fee